reviewText: Would have been much better without the HORRID background music!  It sounds like 3 separate music tracks being played at once!  Sometimes you can hardly hear the narrator because the god awful music is so loud.
I would recommend this to a friend. Interesting plot line interesting characters. I am enjoying it, you probably would, too.

This documentary style video did not light my fire about Iceland.  We are planning a trip to Iceland, and this DVD did little to add to our excitement. It would interest a geologist or a natural history buff more than a traveler.  Probably not worth the price in my view, but it was worth watching once.
